# Cloudflare Pages redirects — applied only when no static file exists
# at the requested path. Static files win; _redirects is the fallback layer.

# Reviews added to R2 after the last site build won't have a SSG page
# at /review/{id}/. Rewrite (200) to the legacy client-fetch route so
# the page still loads (without prerendered title/og tags — that's the
# tradeoff for R2-only updates). See README.md "Iron rule".
/review/:id/  /review/?id=:id  200
